{"title":"MySql常用函数","date":"2020-04-04T15:37:21.409Z","link":"post/369","categories":["MySql"],"updated":"2020-04-04T16:28:06.133Z","content":"<p>date: 2020-04-04 15:42:22</p>\n<h2 id=\"tags-MySql\">tags: MySql<a href=\"post/369#tags-MySql\"></a></h2><h2 id=\"1-字符函数\">1.字符函数<a href=\"post/369#1-字符函数\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"1-1-CONCAT-拼接字符\">1.1 CONCAT 拼接字符<a href=\"post/369#1-1-CONCAT-拼接字符\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select concat(\"hello\",\"world\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| concat(\"hello\",\"world\") |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| helloworld              |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"1-2-LENGTH-获取字节长度\">1.2 LENGTH 获取字节长度<a href=\"post/369#1-2-LENGTH-获取字节长度\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select length(\"hello world\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-----------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| length(\"hello world\") |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-----------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">|                    11 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-----------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select length(\"尚文杰\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+---------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| length(\"尚文杰\")    |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+---------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">|                   9 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+---------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"1-3-CHAR-LENGTH-获取字符长度\">1.3 CHAR_LENGTH 获取字符长度<a href=\"post/369#1-3-CHAR-LENGTH-获取字符长度\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select char_length(\"尚文杰\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+--------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| char_length(\"尚文杰\")    |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+--------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">|                        3 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+--------------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"1-4-SUBSTRING-截取字符串\">1.4 SUBSTRING 截取字符串<a href=\"post/369#1-4-SUBSTRING-截取字符串\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select substr(\"尚文杰\",1,2);</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| substr(\"尚文杰\",1,2)    |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| 尚文                    |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select substr(\"尚文杰\",2);</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-----------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| substr(\"尚文杰\",2)    |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-----------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| 文杰                  |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-----------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"1-5-INSTR-字符第一次出现的位置\">1.5 INSTR 字符第一次出现的位置<a href=\"post/369#1-5-INSTR-字符第一次出现的位置\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select instr(\"尚文杰\",\"尚\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+--------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| instr(\"尚文杰\",\"尚\")     |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+--------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">|                        1 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+--------------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"1-6-TRIM-去前后字符（默认去空格）\">1.6 TRIM 去前后字符（默认去空格）<a href=\"post/369#1-6-TRIM-去前后字符（默认去空格）\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select trim(\" hello world \");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-----------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| trim(\" hello world \") |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-----------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| hello world           |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-----------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select trim(\"x\" from \"xxhello worldxx\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| trim(\"x\" from \"xxhello worldxx\") |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| hello world                      |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"1-7-LPAD-RPAD-左填充-右填充\">1.7 LPAD/RPAD 左填充/右填充<a href=\"post/369#1-7-LPAD-RPAD-左填充-右填充\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select lpad(\"hello\",10,\"x\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| lpad(\"hello\",10,\"x\") |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| xxxxxhello           |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select rpad(\"hello\",10,\"x\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| rpad(\"hello\",10,\"x\") |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| helloxxxxx           |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"1-8-UPPER-LOWER-变大写-变小写\">1.8 UPPER/LOWER 变大写/变小写<a href=\"post/369#1-8-UPPER-LOWER-变大写-变小写\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select upper(\"hello\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| upper(\"hello\") |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| HELLO          |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select lower(\"HELLO\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| lower(\"HELLO\") |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| hello          |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+----------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"1-9-STRCMP-比较\">1.9 STRCMP 比较<a href=\"post/369#1-9-STRCMP-比较\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select strcmp(\"aa\",\"bb\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| strcmp(\"aa\",\"bb\") |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">|                -1 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">select strcmp(\"bb\",\"aa\");</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| strcmp(\"bb\",\"aa\") |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">|                 1 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"1-9-LEFT-RIGHT-左截-右截\">1.9 LEFT/RIGHT 左截/右截<a href=\"post/369#1-9-LEFT-RIGHT-左截-右截\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select left(\"ab\",1);</span><br><span class=\"line\">+--------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| left(\"ab\",1) |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+--------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| a            |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+--------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">select right(\"ab\",1);</span><br><span class=\"line\">+---------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| right(\"ab\",1) |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+---------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| b             |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+---------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","next":{"title":"docker-compose选择启动容器","link":"post/368"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/369/","toc":[{"title":"1.字符函数","id":"1-字符函数","index":"1","children":[{"title":"1.1 CONCAT 拼接字符","id":"1-1-CONCAT-拼接字符","index":"1.1"},{"title":"1.2 LENGTH 获取字节长度","id":"1-2-LENGTH-获取字节长度","index":"1.2"},{"title":"1.3 CHAR_LENGTH 获取字符长度","id":"1-3-CHAR-LENGTH-获取字符长度","index":"1.3"},{"title":"1.4 SUBSTRING 截取字符串","id":"1-4-SUBSTRING-截取字符串","index":"1.4"},{"title":"1.5 INSTR 字符第一次出现的位置","id":"1-5-INSTR-字符第一次出现的位置","index":"1.5"},{"title":"1.6 TRIM 去前后字符（默认去空格）","id":"1-6-TRIM-去前后字符（默认去空格）","index":"1.6"},{"title":"1.7 LPAD/RPAD 左填充/右填充","id":"1-7-LPAD-RPAD-左填充-右填充","index":"1.7"},{"title":"1.8 UPPER/LOWER 变大写/变小写","id":"1-8-UPPER-LOWER-变大写-变小写","index":"1.8"},{"title":"1.9 STRCMP 比较","id":"1-9-STRCMP-比较","index":"1.9"},{"title":"1.9 LEFT/RIGHT 左截/右截","id":"1-9-LEFT-RIGHT-左截-右截","index":"1.10"}]}]}